Package com.google.closure.plugin.proto

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ProtoFinalOptions
    An immutable representation of the same data as ProtoOptions that includes default path information derived from the project configuration.
    ProtoIO
    Protobuf compiler inputs and outputs derived from the proto options and file-system.
    ProtoOptions
    Options for protoc.
    ProtoPackageMap
    Relates proto input files to their package declarations.
    ProtoPackageMap.HashAndPackage
    Bundles the hash and package name for a .proto file.
    ProtoPlanner
    Adds steps that feed .proto files to protoc.
